===Pro Football Hall of Famers===
In the Pro Football Hall of Fame, the Bears are have the most enshrined primary members with twenty-six, however the club also have had five Hall of Famers spend a minor portion of their career with the franchise.<ref>{{cite web | title = Hall of Famers by Team | work = Pro Football Hall of Fame | url = http://www.profootballhof.com/hof/teams.jsp | accessdaymonth = 1 February |accessyear = 2006 }}</ref> George Halas, [[Bronko Nagurski]], and [[Red Grange]] were a part of the original class of inductees in 1963, while defensive end [[Dan Hampton]], the most recent Bear inducted, was a part of the Class of 2002.

