===Retired numbers===
The Bears have retired 13 uniform numbers, which is the most in the NFL, and ranks third behind the basketball [[Boston_Celtics_accomplishments_and_records#Retired_Numbers|Boston Celtics]] (21) and baseball [[New_York_Yankees#Retired_numbers|New York Yankees]] (16) for the most in [[Major North American professional sports leagues|North American professional sports]].
